OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis considers plan  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto dilute partnership      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Lewis is considering a potential  
OL,6, change to its employee-owned business  
OL,7, structure, upending more than 70 years 
OL,8, of tradition.                          
OL,10,FThe group, which also owns Waitrose, is
OL,11,Fcurrently fully owned by its staff, who
OL,12,Freceive a share in the profits.        
OL,14,FBut in the face of tougher trading, the
OL,15,Ffirm is said to be exploring the idea  
OL,16,Fof selling a minority stake.           
OL,18,FThe Sunday Times, which first reported 
OL,19,Fthe move, said the firm hoped to raise 
OL,20,Fup to #2bn.                            
